OL,6,FA man who ordered pizza after stamping
OL,7,Fon the head of his "gentle giant"
OL,8,Ffriend in Nottinghamshire has been
OL,9,Fjailed for life for his murder.
OL,11,FCaine Lonsdale, 34, inflicted 63
OL,12,Fseparate wounds on 40-year-old
OL,13,FJonathan Dittia in Clifton on
OL,14,FSeptember 17 last year.
OL,16,FHe left him dead or dying in the
OL,17,Fliving room of his own flat for an
OL,18,Fhour and a half before calling 999 at
OL,19,F8.32pm and telling the call handler he
OL,20,Fhad "stomped" on the head of his
OL,21,Ffriend.
