OL,3,CMurderer who ordered pizza after
OL,4,Cstamping on friend's head jailed
OL,6,FNottingham Crown Court heard on Friday
OL,7,F(April 25th) that Lonsdale, of
OL,8,FClifton, ordered a pizza delivery to
OL,9,FMr Dittia's flat after he inflicted
OL,10,Fthe fatal wounds, and was seen on CCTV
OL,11,Fcollecting it at the back gate of the
OL,12,Fground-floor flat in Eddleston Drive
OL,13,Fstill wearing blood-stained trainers.
OL,15,FJailing Lonsdale, who wore a grey
OL,16,FAdidas tracksuit and showed no emotion
OL,17,Fin the dock, Judge James Sampson said
OL,18,Fhe must serve at least 15 years before
OL,19,Fhe is eligible for parole for the
OL,20,F"merciless and sustained" attack.
