OL,3,CMurderer who ordered pizza after
OL,4,Cstamping on friend's head jailed
OL,6,FProsecutor Jeremy Janes said Lonsdale
OL,7,Fand Mr Dittia, who was vulnerable and
OL,8,Fhad learning difficulties, were
OL,9,Ffriends and would see each other
OL,10,Fregularly to drink together, each
OL,11,Ftaking it in turns to spend their
OL,12,Fbenefit money on alcohol.
OL,14,FThe court was told a neighbour
OL,15,Freported hearing banging lasting
OL,16,Faround 10 minutes just before 6pm,
OL,17,Fwhich Judge Sampson said must have
OL,18,Fbeen when Lonsdale carried out the
OL,19,Ffatal attack.
