OL,3,CMurderer who ordered pizza after
OL,4,Cstamping on friend's head jailed
OL,6,FAfter murdering his friend, Lonsdale
OL,7,Fwent to his father's address and said:
OL,8,F"Ey up dad, I have killed a mate, or I
OL,9,Fthink I have" before returning to the
OL,10,Fflat and calling 999 after his father
OL,11,Ftold him to.
OL,13,FWhen police arrived, Lonsdale was
OL,14,Foutside the property and was "calm"
OL,15,Fand did not seem drunk, although it
OL,16,Fwas accepted by Judge Sampson that he
OL,17,Fhad been intoxicated at the time of
OL,18,Fthe attack.
