OL,3,CMurderer who ordered pizza after
OL,4,Cstamping on friend's head jailed
OL,6,FAs well as bruises, wounds and
OL,7,Fabrasions to his head, neck and chest,
OL,8,FMr Dittia had a ligature mark around
OL,9,Fhis neck consistent with a phone
OL,10,Fcharging cable that Lonsdale had used
OL,11,Fto "throttle" him, Mr Janes told the
OL,12,Fcourt.
OL,14,F"I am so heartbroken, I would give
OL,15,Fanything to have him back."
OL,17,FIn a victim impact statement, Doris
OL,18,FBrown, Mr Dittia's grandmother, said
OL,19,Fher grandson was a "gentle person with
OL,20,Fa heart of gold."
