OL,3,CMurderer who ordered pizza after
OL,4,Cstamping on friend's head jailed
OL,6,FHis sister, Claire Dittia, said she
OL,7,Fbelieved Lonsdale had exploited her
OL,8,Fbrother's vulnerabilities, adding: "We
OL,9,Fhave all been hit like a tonne of
OL,10,Fbricks.
OL,12,F"My grandmother has lost her smile. I
OL,13,Fam so heartbroken, I would give
OL,14,Fanything to have him back."
OL,16,FStacey Dittia, Mr Dittia's mother,
OL,17,Fsaid: "Despite being a big bloke, he
OL,18,Fwouldn't have hurt a fly."He didn't
OL,19,Fdeserve to die the way he did. No one
OL,20,Fhas the right to take another person's
OL,21,Flife."
