OL,3,CMurderer who ordered pizza after
OL,4,Cstamping on friend's head jailed
OL,6,FDefending, Richard Thatcher said
OL,7,FLonsdale had an IQ of 72 and a "long-
OL,8,Fstanding and chronic" alcohol problem
OL,9,Fthat could have "impaired logical
OL,10,Fthought."
OL,12,FHe told the court: "Whatever it was
OL,13,Fthat triggered that behaviour, he had
OL,14,Fneither the wisdom nor the sobriety to
OL,15,Fdeal with it."
OL,17,FMr Thatcher said Lonsdale has "genuine
OL,18,Fremorse" for what he had done to his
OL,19,Ffriend of many years and that he had
OL,20,Fnot intended to kill him.
