OL,3,CMurderer who ordered pizza after
OL,4,Cstamping on friend's head jailed
OL,6,FSentencing him, Judge Sampson said:
OL,7,F"You say you cannot now remember the
OL,8,Fincident, but it was a merciless and
OL,9,Fsustained attack on a defenceless man.
OL,11,F"You were intoxicated and this was
OL,12,Falmost certainly a disinhibitor. You
OL,13,Fused your shod foot as a weapon and
OL,14,Fthe sustained nature of the attack
OL,15,Fmust have resulted in mental and
OL,16,Fphysical harm to Mr Dittia.
OL,18,F"This took place in his own home,
OL,19,Fwhere he should have been safe.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
