OL,6,F"Although you have a very low IQ and
OL,7,Fhave suffered anxiety and depression,
OL,8,Fthere was no disability which lowered
OL,9,Fyour culpability."
OL,11,FHe said the 216 days Lonsdale has
OL,12,Falready been in custody will be taken
OL,13,Foff the sentence he must serve.
